'''Erwithat Spaceport''' was the main [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] in the city of [[Erwithat (city)|Erwithat]] on [[Pembric II]]. The ground of the spaceport was wet sand rather than [[Permacrete/Legends|permacrete]], and the buildings were made of stone. Predominantly white, the buildings were covered in mold and dirt. In [[8 ABY/Legends|8 ABY]], the spaceport was constantly besieged by desperate civilians trying to get off-world. They were treated badly by the [[Pembric Security Legion]], who often used violence to quell their protests. It was under the control of [[Erwithat Space Control]]. It contained [[Landing Pad 28]] and [[Pad 642]].

